show.description: Ek powerful comeback ki kahaani jahan betrayal, revenge aur ambition takraate hain. Maria, past ke dard aur politics ke jungle mein apna raasta banati hai. Slay Madam ek gripping ride hai jo dikhata hai ki asli power kis ke paas hoti hai! Abhi dekhiye poora drama.
